### 340.

From the chin to the roots of the hair is 1/10 of the whole figure. From
the joint of the palm of the hand to the tip of the longest finger is
1/10. From the chin to the top of the head 1/8; and from the pit of the
stomach to the top of the breast is 1/6, and from the pit below the
breast bone to the top of the head 1/4. From the chin to the nostrils
1/3 Part of the face, the same from the nostrils to the brow and from
the brow to the roots of the hair, and the foot is 1/6, the elbow 1/4,
the width of the shoulders 1/4.

